You heard us wrong.

8
00:01:07,300 --> 00:01:08,800
Mom.

9
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:12,070
You just said it right now.

10
00:01:12,070 --> 00:01:15,530
That she gave birth to me and left me at our door.

11
00:01:18,210 --> 00:01:23,270
Pil Sung, Pil Sung, no, I...

12
00:01:23,270 --> 00:01:27,200
Hey! How dare you call his name?

13
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,770
How dare you call his name?

14
00:01:28,770 --> 00:01:31,530
