170
00:12:48,420 --> 00:12:51,570
You can't bring yourself to admit it.

171
00:12:53,210 --> 00:12:55,540
It must be true.

172
00:13:01,670 --> 00:13:03,450
I'm sorry.

173
00:13:05,630 --> 00:13:07,960
I'm sorry, Pil Sung.

174
00:13:11,160 --> 00:13:13,120
Sorry?

175
00:13:15,140 --> 00:13:18,350
Do you think saying sorry is enough?

176
00:13:22,870 --> 00:13:27,070
I really had no choice then.

177
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:31,600
I was in a situation where I had no other choice.

178
00:13:34,040 --> 00:13:40,720
What situation would make you... abandon a baby who was born less than a week ago?

179
00:13:41,630 --> 00:13:46,440
What reason would make you abandon a baby?

180
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:48,090
At a friend's house, even.

181
00:13:48,090 --> 00:13:51,500
I wanted to see you that way.

182
00:13:51,500 --> 00:13:54,630
I wanted to make sure you were being raised safely.

183
00:13:54,630 --> 00:13:56,400
That's why I...

184
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:58,190
How...

185
00:13:59,170 --> 00:14:02,250
could you be so selfish until the end?

186
00:14:02,790 --> 00:14:05,360
You call that an excuse?

187
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,550
Pil Sung.

188
00:14:06,550 --> 00:14:10,090
So...you could see me whenever you want,

189
00:14:10,090 --> 00:14:13,480
you abandoned me with your friend, my mom?

190
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:15,900
Do you only care about your feelings?

191
00:14:15,900 --> 00:14:20,800
Do you not care about my mom, who thought of you as her friend?

192
00:14:20,800 --> 00:14:23,940
You think only your feelings matter?

193
00:14:23,940 --> 00:14:29,830
Have you ever thought about how much hurt and betrayed my mom would feel?

194
00:14:29,830 --> 00:14:34,090
How can you only think about your feelings? How?

195
00:14:35,010 --> 00:14:36,850
I'm sorry.

196
00:14:36,850 --> 00:14:38,940
I'm sorry, Pil Sung.

197
00:14:38,940 --> 00:14:41,560
I really deserve to die.

198
00:14:58,250 --> 00:15:01,060
I'm sorry, Pil Sung.

199
00:15:04,810 --> 00:15:08,830
