201
00:15:12,370 --> 00:15:17,170
He can't just not come home just because he's upset.

202
00:15:17,170 --> 00:15:20,510
Mom, do you think he's a child? He's old enough.

203
00:15:20,510 --> 00:15:22,830
He'll come home.

204
00:15:22,830 --> 00:15:26,470
By the way, why did our old tenant's grandma

205
00:15:26,470 --> 00:15:30,040
have to show up then and confuse us?

206
00:15:30,040 --> 00:15:31,800
I know.

207
00:15:31,800 --> 00:15:34,920
