208
00:15:34,920 --> 00:15:38,620
He had to care for that lady while he was in shock.

209
00:15:38,620 --> 00:15:40,670
I'm worried, too.

210
00:15:42,340 --> 00:15:45,630
Hey! Pil Sung!

211
00:15:45,630 --> 00:15:48,000
Gosh, Pil Sung.

212
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:50,460
Where have you been all this time?

213
00:15:50,460 --> 00:15:55,780
We were so worried that you left like that.

214
00:15:55,780 --> 00:15:58,240
I'm sorry. I had to take care of something.

215
00:15:58,240 --> 00:16:00,110
Where's Mom?

216
00:16:00,110 --> 00:16:02,090
Your mom...

217
00:16:02,090 --> 00:16:05,890
She's in bed because she's in shock.

218
00:16:14,130 --> 00:16:15,860
Pil Sung.

219
00:16:15,860 --> 00:16:19,260
Honey, Pil Sung's here.

220
00:16:23,980 --> 00:16:28,380
Pil Sung, are you okay?

221
00:16:28,380 --> 00:16:31,460
Of course, I'm okay.

222
00:16:33,290 --> 00:16:38,430
Pil Sung, you must've been so shocked earlier.

223
00:16:39,980 --> 00:16:42,050
I'm sorry.

224
00:16:42,800 --> 00:16:49,060
I didn't want you to see me like that, but you did in the end.

225
00:16:50,750 --> 00:16:53,070
I'm so sorry.

226
00:16:54,230 --> 00:16:57,990
Don't apologize. Why would you say that?

227
00:16:57,990 --> 00:17:00,380
I'm worried about you.

228
00:17:01,020 --> 00:17:03,370
No, no.

229
00:17:03,370 --> 00:17:06,300
I'm just sorry about everything.

230
00:17:06,300 --> 00:17:08,810
I was foolish.

231
00:17:09,670 --> 00:17:15,330
You had to see me like that because I'm a foolish mom.

232
00:17:15,330 --> 00:17:20,830
Mom, Father, I'm really okay.

233
00:17:22,260 --> 00:17:28,960
You're the only mom to me in this world.

234
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:30,920
You're the only one.

235
00:17:33,020 --> 00:17:35,140
My Pil Sung,

236
00:17:35,760 --> 00:17:38,090
my son.

237
00:17:38,090 --> 00:17:40,860
Thank you for saying that.

238
00:17:42,140 --> 00:17:45,880
I'm so upset I could die.

239
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:49,450
It wasn't even a stranger. How...

240
00:17:49,450 --> 00:17:52,390
How could Soo Yeon do that...

241
00:17:53,760 --> 00:17:56,280
Honey, but still.

242
00:17:56,280 --> 00:17:59,300
Don't say that in front of Pil Sung.

243
00:17:59,300 --> 00:18:01,920
You're making him upset.

244
00:18:04,470 --> 00:18:06,890
I'm sorry, Pil Sung.

245
00:18:09,250 --> 00:18:15,690
Because you're such an important person to me,

246
00:18:15,690 --> 00:18:19,520
I always wondered who gave birth to you,

247
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:22,920
and I was always so grateful to her.

248
00:18:22,920 --> 00:18:26,780
If she ended up visiting you,

249
00:18:26,780 --> 00:18:30,390
I was going to thank her sincerely.

250
00:18:31,830 --> 00:18:33,510
But...

251
00:18:34,320 --> 00:18:37,210
But I didn't think this would happen.

252
00:18:38,260 --> 00:18:40,790
I can't be like this.

253
00:18:40,790 --> 00:18:44,510
I really thought of her as my friend.

254
00:18:44,510 --> 00:18:49,130
She approached me ever since you were young, deceived me and lied to me.

255
00:18:49,130 --> 00:18:52,150
Thinking that...

256
00:18:52,150 --> 00:18:54,470
I really...

257
00:18:54,470 --> 00:18:59,080
I really can't forgive her.

258
00:18:59,080 --> 00:19:05,610
I... I really wish I could...

259
00:19:05,610 --> 00:19:07,990
I really...

260
00:19:10,940 --> 00:19:13,290
I'm sorry, Pil Sung.

261
00:19:15,170 --> 00:19:16,920
Mom,

262
00:19:17,600 --> 00:19:20,950
I can't forgive her for hurting you so much, either.

263
00:19:20,950 --> 00:19:24,780
So, you do whatever you want to do.

264
00:19:25,980 --> 00:19:27,840
Pil Sung...

265
00:19:35,100 --> 00:19:36,950
My son...

266
00:19:41,750 --> 00:19:43,860
Pil Sung.

267
00:19:43,860 --> 00:19:46,320
My Pil Sung...

268
00:19:46,320 --> 00:19:48,170
My son.

